00:09:32,660 --> 00:09:34,700
Get stuck in here, huh?

132
00:09:34,790 --> 00:09:38,500
- Mommy, what happened?
- Sorry. It's all right.

133
00:09:38,620 --> 00:09:41,920
Dammit.
