516
00:38:10,090 --> 00:38:11,960
and then I was rushing,
and I forgot it.

517
00:38:12,050 --> 00:38:14,090
- It's OK.
- Sorry.

518
00:38:15,590 --> 00:38:17,930
- What did you think of your teacher?
- She was very nice.

519
00:38:18,050 --> 00:38:20,470
