758
01:00:15,330 --> 01:00:18,120
I love them, Mommy.

759
01:00:18,250 --> 01:00:20,500
I'm glad.

760
01:00:20,580 --> 01:00:22,460
Mm.

761
01:00:23,340 --> 01:00:25,750
I love you, Mommy.

762
01:00:25,840 --> 01:00:28,340
You haven't said anything
