775
01:01:17,810 --> 01:01:19,930
Yeah.

776
01:01:33,740 --> 01:01:38,120
I love you, Mommy.
Thank you for taking care of me.

777
01:02:05,690 --> 01:02:07,730
Ceci?

778
01:02:17,620 --> 01:02:20,830
- Hello?
- Mommy, where were you?

779
