and we'll sort this out. All right?

884
01:09:44,310 --> 01:09:45,730
Yeah. Absolutely.

885
01:09:51,490 --> 01:09:53,860
Get down!

886
01:10:18,350 --> 01:10:21,350
This time make sure
you put it in the garbage truck.

887
01:10:21,430 --> 01:10:23,560
- Where did you...
