01:29:11,560 --> 01:29:15,320
Don't leave me.
I want you to be my mommy.

1111
01:29:15,400 --> 01:29:17,990
- Don't leave me.
- Ceci!

1112
01:29:18,070 --> 01:29:20,610
You can't leave me.

1113
01:29:23,410 --> 01:29:25,370
Ceci!

1114
01:29:25,580 --> 01:29:27,580
Ceci!

