Ceci.

1150
01:34:57,330 --> 01:34:58,790
Ceci?

1151
01:34:59,080 --> 01:35:00,000
Ceci?

1152
01:35:00,080 --> 01:35:02,410
Open the door.
Push the button, Ceci.

1153
01:35:02,500 --> 01:35:05,380
Open it. Open the door. Ceci!

1154
01:35:34,610 --> 01:35:36,950
My beautiful girl.

